16) I seem to be missing some library functions.  Where should usleep be?

usleep is a system function on Suns which you might not have.  It's
unimportant for the functionality of xlincks and therefore it is made
optional.  Make sure you have the EXTRA_DEFINES set to the right thing
for your architecture.  It should not have -DHAVE_USLEEP in it.

