25) I can't get cutoff to work.  What's going on?

Cutoff is a tricky beast.  Note that you MUST:

cd DBDIR
mkdir Archive
cp * Archive/

before you run cutoff.  If you don't make the Archive directory and
copy all of the files, cutoff won't work.  If you have done this, and
it still doesn't work, then the problem is a new one, so please send us
mail.  How to run cutoff is in the cutoff man page.

